Press Release: Jedit v1.0 for macOS \'97 A Free, Full-Featured Rich Text Editor on the Mac App Store\
\
Dear Editor,\
\
Thank you for your time.\
My name is Satoshi Matsumoto, representative of\
Artman21 Inc. (
\f0 \'8d\'87\'8e\'91\'89\'ef\'8e\'d0\'83\'41\'81\'5b\'83\'67\'83\'7d\'83\'93\'93\'f3\'88\'eb
\f1 ) in Japan.\
We are pleased to announce the release of Jedit v1.0,\
a free text editor for macOS, on the Mac App Store on\
April 19, 2026. I am writing to share the press release\
with you.\
