\uc0\u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \u9473 \

\f0 \'81\'9f
\f1  A ground-up rewrite, succeeding Jedit \uc0\u937 \
  Jedit \uc0\u937  was loved by Mac users in Japan for many\
  years, but its aging codebase could no longer keep up\
  with newer versions of macOS. Sales and support for\
  Jedit \uc0\u937  ended at the end of November 2025. The new\
  Jedit is its successor \'97 a general-purpose text editor\
  rewritten from scratch, using Jedit \uc0\u937  as a reference.\

\f0 \'81\'9f
\f1  Developed with AI (Claude Code) throughout\
  The rewrite adopted the Claude Code AI coding\
  assistant across the entire development process,\
  enabling a rapid transition to a modern Swift /\
  AppKit codebase.\

\f0 \'81\'9f
\f1  Optimized for Japanese and English authoring\
  Supports plain text, RTF, RTFD, Microsoft Word, and\
  Markdown. Features include vertical text layout,\
  automatic detection of a wide range of Japanese\
  encodings, careful CJK typography, regex find /\
  replace, iCloud Drive sync, and full AppleScript\
  support \'97 covering the daily needs of writers and\
  professionals.\

\f0 \'81\'9f
